WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:10.424 --> 00:00:14.939
 Today Spitzbeingulasch is (Sulzpaprikasch) prepared. 

00:00:16.414 --> 00:00:17.829
 Ingredients: 5. 0:19 - 0:21 

00:00:18.639 --> 00:00:21.314
 1.5 kg pig feet (pointed legs), 

00:00:21.907 --> 00:00:23.640
 200 g fat, 

00:00:24.896 --> 00:00:27.260
 2 large onions, 3 garlic cloves, 

00:00:28.784 --> 00:00:30.975
 half a glass of homemade Letscho, 9th 0:33 - 0:36 

00:00:33.242 --> 00:00:36.312
 if not available: 1 pepper, 1 tomato, 

00:00:37.443 --> 00:00:39.486
 2 tablespoons tomato paste, 

00:00:40.401 --> 00:00:42.234
 1 tablespoon salt, 

00:00:43.093 --> 00:00:45.671
 2 tablespoons of paprika, 13. 0:47 - 0:50 

00:00:46.954 --> 00:00:49.545
 1 teaspoon of ground cumin, 

00:00:50.217 --> 00:00:52.808
 1 hot pepper. 

00:00:55.050 --> 00:01:01.378
 The detailed recipe please look at: www.nemzetikonyha.hu 16. 1:05 - 1:08 

00:01:04.540 --> 00:01:08.410
 Preparation: Chop the onions. 

00:01:11.340 --> 00:01:15.027
 Mince garlic. 

00:01:41.946 --> 00:01:47.010
 Let grease melt in the kettle. 19. 2:09 - 2:14 

00:02:08.574 --> 00:02:13.805
 Add onions. 20. 2:32 - 2:36 

00:02:31.549 --> 00:02:36.302
 Only fry until glassy. 

00:02:50.344 --> 00:02:54.374
 Add tomato paste. 

00:03:00.564 --> 00:03:04.341
 Then salt is added. 

00:03:17.491 --> 00:03:21.089
 Sprinkle with paprika. 

00:03:47.322 --> 00:03:51.473
 Dilute with water. 25. 3:55 - 4:01 

00:03:54.634 --> 00:04:01.484
 Add cleaned and split pork feet. 

00:04:25.872 --> 00:04:30.700
 Pour enough water over it to cover it. 27. 4:57 - 5:00 

00:04:56.911 --> 00:04:59.739
 Simmer with the lid closed and low heat for 45 minutes. 28. 5:06 - 5:10 

00:05:06.389 --> 00:05:09.754
 Letscho pour over it. 29. 5:12 - 5:16 

00:05:12.231 --> 00:05:15.634
 Then add ground cumin. 30. 5:21 - 5:24 

00:05:20.614 --> 00:05:23.964
 Stir everything. 

00:05:32.755 --> 00:05:35.297
 Continue cooking with the lid closed. 32. 5:38 - 5:43 

00:05:37.826 --> 00:05:42.722
 When half of the stock is boiled, remove the lid. 

00:05:48.045 --> 00:05:52.724
 Simmer for another half hour with a small fire. 

00:06:18.820 --> 00:06:26.795
 Serve with boiled potatoes. 35. 6:40 - 6:43 

00:06:40.203 --> 00:06:43.310
 We wish you a good appetite! 36. 6:47 - 6:52 

00:06:46.846 --> 00:06:52.317
 Let us preserve our traditions! 

